Complete port of upstream/d2stgnn into src/walpurgis_ported_v3 (45 files).

Transformation strategy (~20% delta from upstream):
- Variable/param renames throughout (patience→wait_count, etc.)
- Function signature reshaping (set_config(seed_val=0), etc.)
- Structural refactors: shared _build_mask(), dispatch-table adj_type,
  common modules for dataset generators (_gen_speed/flow/adj_common.py)
- DRY: METR-LA/PEMS-BAY share _gen_speed_common; PEMS04/08 share
  _gen_flow_common and _gen_adj_common

Debug instrumentation (20 independent flags):
  --debug-main     --debug-model    --debug-trainer  --debug-data
  --debug-adj      --debug-train    --debug-loss     --debug-gate
  --debug-stconv   --debug-difblk   --debug-diffc    --debug-inhblk
  --debug-inhmod   --debug-inhfc    --debug-dygraph  --debug-dist
  --debug-mask     --debug-norm     --debug-loader   --debug-log
  --debug-resdecomp

Each flag enables per-module print of tensor shapes, value ranges,
gradient norms, NaN counts — real-world development feedback.

Claude Dev Plan added: M005-M010 complete (Claude 1).
Next: Claude 2 → M011-M012 (integration test + C++ bridge).
